content:
OmniScripts Password Element

Enable users to enter a password by adding the Password element to your OmniScript. Set the minimum and maximum lengths of the password.

Drag a Password element from the Build panel onto the canvas.
In the Properties panel, give the element a name in the Name field.
In Field Label, enter a label visible to the user.
In Minimum Password Length, enter the minimum number of characters the user must enter for a valid password.
In Maximum Password Length, set the maximum number of characters the user can enter for a valid password.

Password Properties

Password properties are configurable from the Properties panel when you select a Password element.
title: OmniScripts Password Element Configuration
